#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo empowers you to manage every aspect of your construction projects "
"effortlessly and efficiently, and its integrated applications ensure "
"unparalleled success and client satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຄຸ້ມຄອງທຸກພາກສ່ວນຂອງໂຄງການກໍ່ສ້າງຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, "
"ດ້ວຍແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນ ເຊິ່ງຈະຮັບປະກັນຄວາມສຳເລັດ ແລະ ຄວາມພຶງພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo offers scalable solutions that grow with your business. By integrating "
"these apps,\n"
"            construction companies can maximize efficiency, improve client "
"relations, and reduce\n"
"            operational risks."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ສະໜອງທາງເລືອກທີ່ປັບຂະໜາດໄດ້ຕາມການເຕີບໂຕຂອງທຸລະກິດ. ໂດຍການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແອັບເຫຼົ່ານີ້,\n"
"            ບໍລິສັດກໍ່ສ້າງສາມາດເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບສູງສຸດ, ປັບປຸງຄວາມສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ, ແລະ ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນ\n"
"            ຄວາມສ່ຽງໃນການດຳເນີນງານ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo scans every component within your Work Items to find underlying needs, "
"filtering components by the Material Cost Nature, ensuring your list isn't "
"cluttered with labor or equipment hours."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຈະກວດສອບທຸກອົງປະກອບໃນລາຍການວຽກຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອຄົ້ນຫາຄວາມຕ້ອງການທີ່ແທ້ຈິງ, "
"ໂດຍກັ່ນຕອງອົງປະກອບຕາມລັກສະນະຕົ້ນທຶນວັດສະດຸ, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າລາຍການຂອງທ່ານຈະບໍ່ປົນກັບຊົ່ວໂມງແຮງງານ "
"ຫຼື ອຸປະກອນ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, these default tasks can be adapted in the\n"
"                    Project Template according to your personal way of "
"managing a construction\n"
"                    project."
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນວ່າ, ວຽກມາດຕະຖານເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດປັບປ່ຽນໄດ້ໃນ\n"
"                    ແບບຟອມໂຄງການ ຕາມວິທີການຄຸ້ມຄອງໂຄງການກໍ່ສ້າງ\n"
"                    ໃນແບບຂອງທ່ານເອງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free\n"
"            to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything "
"around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນວ່າ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດ\n"
"            ເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ!"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "On confirmation, the sale order is associated to your project!"
msgstr "ເມື່ອຍືນຍັນ, ໃບສັ່ງຊາຍຈະຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໂຄງການຂອງທ່ານທັນທີ!"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "On purchase order confirmation."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຍືນຍັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On sale order confirmation, the project template is duplicated for the new "
"project to\n"
"            start (triggered by the Project Management product). \n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            It comes with some predefined tasks and some additional ones "
"directly coming\n"
"            from the sold products:"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຍືນຍັນໃບສັ່ງຊາຍ, ແບບຟອມໂຄງການຈະຖືກສຳເນົາເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໂຄງການໃໝ່\n"
"            (ເລີ່ມໂດຍສິນຄ້າປະເພດການຄຸ້ມຄອງໂຄງການ). \n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            ມັນຈະມາພ້ອມກັບວຽກທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ ແລະ ວຽກເພີ່ມເຕີມບາງຢ່າງທີ່ມາຈາກ\n"
"            ສິນຄ້າທີ່ຂາຍໄປໂດຍກົງ:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "On vendor bill confirmation."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຍືນຍັນໃບເກັບເງິນຈາກຜູ້ສະໜອງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once approved, come back, select those lines and trigger the delivery\n"
"                update.<br/>This will update sale order to capture those "
"increments and create a\n"
"                draft invoice."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອໄດ້ຮັບການອະນຸມັດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ກັບມາເລືອກລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ ແລະ ກົດອັບເດດການສົ່ງມອບ\n"
"                .<br/>ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະອັບເດດໃບສັ່ງຊາຍເພື່ອບັນທຶກສ່ວນເພີ່ມເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ ແລະ ສ້າງ\n"
"                ໃບເກັບເງິນຮ່າງຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once confirmed, the quotation becomes a sales order."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຍືນຍັນແລ້ວ, ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຈະກາຍເປັນໃບສັ່ງຊາຍ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open again the Product Variants list, select them all and proceed to an\n"
"                        (import-compatible) export with only their names"
msgstr ""
"ເປີດລາຍການສິນຄ້າຍ່ອຍ (Product Variants) ອີກຄັ້ງ, ເລືອກທັງໝົດ ແລະ ທຳການ\n"
"                        ສົ່ງອອກ (ແບບຮອງຮັບການນຳເຂົ້າ) ໂດຍເລືອກສະເພາະຊື່ຂອງພວກມັນ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open now the Taxes still from the configuration menu."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູ ພາສີ (Taxes) ຈາກເມນູການຕັ້ງຄ່າ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Other Info tab and in the Invoicing section, adjust the Contract "
"Type per your needs."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດແຖບ ຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນໆ (Other Info) ແລະ ໃນສ່ວນການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ, ໃຫ້ປັບປຸງ ປະເພດສັນຍາ "
"ຕາມຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Product Variants list and proceed to import of the \"1. Product\n"
"                        Variants Import\" sheet"
msgstr "ເປີດລາຍການສິນຄ້າຍ່ອຍ ແລະ ທຳການນຳເຂົ້າແຜ່ນງານ \"1. Product Variants Import\""

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Progress view. It captures all sale order lines associated to this "
"project."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດມຸມມອງ ຄວາມຄືບໜ້າ (Progress). ມັນຈະສະແດງທຸກລາຍການໃບສັ່ງຊາຍທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບໂຄງການນີ້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Work Items list and proceed to import of the \"3. Work Items "
"Import\"\n"
"                        sheet"
msgstr ""
"ເປີດລາຍການວຽກ (Work Items) ແລະ ທຳການນຳເຂົ້າແຜ່ນງານ \"3. Work Items Import\""

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the contact form of your contact eligible to the tax discount "
"associated to this fiscal position."
msgstr "ເປີດແບບຟອມຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ຂອງລູກຄ້າທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບສິດຫຼຸດພາສີ ເຊິ່ງເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບສະຖານະທາງພາສີນັ້ນ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the project dashboard and create new updates to capture progress in "
"terms of:"
msgstr "ເປີດແດຊບອດໂຄງການ ແລະ ສ້າງການອັບເດດໃໝ່ເພື່ອບັນທຶກຄວາມຄືບໜ້າໃນສ່ວນຂອງ:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
