msgstr "ແບບທາງເຕັກນິກ & ການສຶກສາ "

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>CRM module</strong> helps construction companies capture leads "
"from multiple\n"
"            sources, track communications, and schedule follow-ups.  <br/"
">You can prioritize\n"
"            high-value opportunities and turn inquiries into profitable "
"projects."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໂມດູນ CRM</strong> ຊ່ວຍບໍລິສັດກໍ່ສ້າງໃນການຊອກຫາລູກຄ້າໃໝ່ຈາກຫຼາຍ\n"
"            ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ, ຕິດຕາມການສື່ສານ, ແລະ ວາງແຜນການຕິດຕາມຜົນ. <br/>ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດລຳດັບ\n"
"            ໂອກາດທີ່ມີມູນຄ່າສູງ ແລະ ປ່ຽນການສອບຖາມໃຫ້ເປັນໂຄງການທີ່ສ້າງກຳໄລໄດ້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Field Service App</strong> helps you manage on-site "
"interventions such as\n"
"            follow-up works, warranty services, or urgent client requests. "
"Technicians can access\n"
"            tasks, log hours, and report outcomes directly from their mobile "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບການບໍລິການພາກສະໜາມ</strong> ຊ່ວຍທ່ານຄຸ້ມຄອງການລົງໜ້າວຽກ ເຊັ່ນ\n"
"            ວຽກຕິດຕາມຜົນ, ການບໍລິການຫຼັງການຂາຍ, ຫຼື ຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍດ່ວນຈາກລູກຄ້າ. "
"ຊ່າງເຕັກນິກສາມາດເຂົ້າເບິ່ງ\n"
"            ວຽກ, ບັນທຶກຊົ່ວໂມງ, ແລະ ລາຍງານຜົນໄດ້ໂດຍກົງຈາກມືຖື."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Planning app</strong> schedules tasks, allocates employees, and "
"coordinates\n"
"            equipment use across multiple construction sites."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບການວາງແຜນ</strong> ຈັດຕາຕະລາງວຽກ, ຈັດສັນພະນັກງານ, ແລະ ປະສານງານ\n"
"            ການໃຊ້ອຸປະກອນໃນຫຼາຍສະຖານທີ່ກໍ່ສ້າງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Projects App</strong> allows you to manage tasks, assign "
"resources, and\n"
"            create milestones for each construction project."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບໂຄງການ</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຄຸ້ມຄອງວຽກ, ມອບໝາຍຊັບພະຍາກອນ, ແລະ\n"
"            ສ້າງຂັ້ນຕອນສຳເລັດ (Milestones) ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະໂຄງການກໍ່ສ້າງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Sales App</strong> enables rapid creation of professional "
"quotations.\n"
"            You can use product kits for materials, apply discounts, and "
"send polished proposals\n"
"            directly to clients."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບການຂາຍ</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາແບບມືອາຊີບໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ.\n"
"            ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຊຸດສິນຄ້າສຳລັບວັດສະດຸ, ນຳໃຊ້ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ, ແລະ ສົ່ງຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ສວຍງາມ\n"
"            ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "The construction industries come in two parts:"
msgstr "ອຸດສາຫະກຳການກໍ່ສ້າງແບ່ງອອກເປັນສອງສ່ວນ:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The module comes of top of the Construction Builder setup "
"providing additional capabilities."
msgstr "ໂມດູນນີ້ເປັນສ່ວນເສີມຈາກການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Construction Builder ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄວາມສາມາດໃຫ້ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,description_sale:construction.product_product_6_product_template
msgid ""
"The prepared mortar is a dry, industrially premixed masonry mortar in "
