#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Typically, work items products are priced in a scale-able fashion and billed "
"based on\n"
"            delivered quantity.<br/>Those are defined as service products "
"with invoicing based on\n"
"            manual delivery."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍທົ່ວໄປແລ້ວ, ລາຍການວຽກຈະຖືກຕັ້ງລາຄາແບບປັບຂະໜາດໄດ້ ແລະ ເກັບເງິນຕາມ\n"
"            ຈຳນວນທີ່ສົ່ງມອບ.<br/>ລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຖືກກຳນົດເປັນສິນຄ້າບໍລິການ ທີ່ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນຕາມ\n"
"            ການສົ່ງມອບທີ່ປ້ອນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
