msgstr "ທໍ່ນ້ຳເຂົ້າ, ອ່າງດັກໄຂມັນ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"We setup an automation so that your product costs and purchase opportunities "
"reflect your last purchases as follow:"
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຕົ້ນທຶນສິນຄ້າ ແລະ "
"ໂອກາດການຈັດຊື້ສະທ້ອນເຖິງການຊື້ຄັ້ງຫຼ້າສຸດຂອງທ່ານ ດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When ordering materials and services, fill in the analytic distribution to "
"wire\n"
"                    the expenses to specific projects."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສັ່ງຊື້ວັດສະດຸ ແລະ ການບໍລິການ, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນການແຈກຢາຍການວິເຄາະ (Analytic Distribution) "
"ເພື່ອ\n"
"                    ສົ່ງຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍໄປຫາໂຄງການສະເພາະນັ້ນໆ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When progress increment is reflecting the situation, select one of the lines "
"and hit\n"
"                the Generate Report button.<br/>You now have a progress "
"report ready to send to\n"
"                the approver (defined from the project if not the customer)."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສ່ວນເພີ່ມຄວາມຄືບໜ້າສະທ້ອນເຖິງສະຖານະຕົວຈິງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກລາຍການໃດໜຶ່ງ ແລ້ວກົດ\n"
"                ປຸ່ມ ສ້າງລາຍງານ (Generate Report).<br/"
">ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານມີລາຍງານຄວາມຄືບໜ້າທີ່ພ້ອມຈະສົ່ງໃຫ້\n"
